399
00:12:38,020 --> 00:12:38,590
Right?

400
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:39,310
Chen.

401
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:40,140
Calm down.

402
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:40,860
These children

403
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:41,780
