What's the matter?

586
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,250
Is Qi Qi asleep?

587
00:20:39,675 --> 00:20:41,190
She got a message from Song Cong,

588
00:20:41,190 --> 00:20:42,720
saying they're going on a date tomorrow.

589
00:20:42,725 --> 00:20:44,050
She's taking her beauty sleep.

590
00:20:45,540 --> 00:20:46,060
Did you ask

591
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:48,375
what did she argue with her mom about?

592
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,670
She wants to switch
to a literature major.

593
00:20:50,728 --> 00:20:51,470
Her mom disagreed,

594
00:20:51,672 --> 00:20:52,710
so they had an argument.

595
00:20:55,100 --> 00:20:56,500
You must admit that Qi Qi

596
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:57,540
is pretty opinionated.

597
00:20:58,300 --> 00:20:59,864
She confessed in front of everyone

598
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,990
that she was dating Song Cong.

599
00:21:02,168 --> 00:21:03,320
She's quite brave.

600
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:04,470
She is indeed brave.

601
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:08,340
Mom.

602
00:21:10,340 --> 00:21:11,540
If a girl

603
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:13,100
has someone she likes,

604
00:21:14,024 --> 00:21:15,390
should she take the initiative?

605
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:16,540
Of course.

606
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:19,190
Huan'er, I'm telling you.

607
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:21,190
It's not easy

608
00:21:21,580 --> 00:21:22,950
to meet the right person

609
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:23,910
in your life.

610
00:21:24,540 --> 00:21:25,390
Once you meet one,

611
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:26,470
go after him.

612
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,060
Girls taking the initiative

613
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:28,670
isn't shameful.

614
00:21:32,670 --> 00:21:33,100
Huan'er.

615
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,780
Young people nowadays

616
00:21:35,340 --> 00:21:36,340
are more open-minded.

617
00:21:36,632 --> 00:21:38,060
After you start a relationship,

618
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:39,020
you must remember

619
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,820
to protect yourself.

620
00:21:40,990 --> 00:21:41,950
Take safety measures.

621
00:21:41,970 --> 00:21:43,589
And all that stuff about a safe period

622
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:44,419
- is nonsense.
- Mom.

623
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:45,384
You can't believe it.

624
00:21:45,384 --> 00:21:46,584
I don't have a boyfriend.

625
00:21:46,664 --> 00:21:47,870
Why are you telling me this?

626
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:48,820
Well...

627
00:21:49,470 --> 00:21:50,430
I have a lot

628
00:21:50,430 --> 00:21:51,060
to tell you.

629
00:21:51,470 --> 00:21:52,390
I'll tell you

630
00:21:52,390 --> 00:21:53,340
as early as I can.

631
00:21:53,340 --> 00:21:54,670
Or what if I don't have time?

632
00:21:55,544 --> 00:21:56,664
You don't have time?

633
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:01,430
Nothing.

634
00:22:02,780 --> 00:22:03,190
Go to bed.

635
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:05,020
Good night, Mom.

636
00:22:19,390 --> 00:22:20,060
The fifth row.

637
00:22:20,870 --> 00:22:21,780
This outfit

638
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:22,710
doesn't look like yours.

639
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:25,160
I'm wearing Huan'er's clothes.

640
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:27,100
You haven't made up with Aunt yet?

641
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:28,500
No.

642
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:41,260
I didn't expect you

643
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:43,200
to ask me out to watch a movie.

644
00:22:46,100 --> 00:22:46,630
Qi Qi.

645
00:22:48,630 --> 00:22:49,540
I will try my best

646
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:50,750
to be your boyfriend.

647
00:22:51,780 --> 00:22:54,540
But this is my first time
being someone's boyfriend.

648
00:22:55,020 --> 00:22:57,230
So if there's anything
I'm not doing well,

649
00:22:57,230 --> 00:22:58,325
you have to tell me.

650
00:22:58,580 --> 00:22:59,470
Sure.

651
00:22:59,910 --> 00:23:01,190
But you need to think it through.

652
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,430
I have high requirements.

653
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:06,060
I'll try my best.

654
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:07,870
I'm just kidding.

655
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:09,340
Actually,

656
00:23:09,670 --> 00:23:10,670
I'm content

657
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:11,825
as long as the two of us

658
00:23:12,950 --> 00:23:14,190
can be together.

659
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:21,340
I had a chat

660
00:23:21,340 --> 00:23:22,430
with my dad last night.

661
00:23:23,190 --> 00:23:24,100
They're supportive

662
00:23:24,150 --> 00:23:25,025
of our relationship.

663
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:25,670
Really?

664
00:23:26,390 --> 00:23:27,710
You even told your dad?

665
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:28,190
Yes.

666
00:23:32,975 --> 00:23:34,275
Here's a reward.

667
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:40,525
Have you told your mom?

668
00:23:43,230 --> 00:23:43,780
I...

669
00:23:44,910 --> 00:23:46,190
I haven't.

670
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:50,950
Let's watch the movie.

671
00:24:31,630 --> 00:24:33,650
Song Cong,
time for Chinese New Year's Eve dinner.

672
00:24:34,190 --> 00:24:34,540
Coming.

673
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:43,820
Food is coming.

674
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:45,100
Mom, stop busying yourself.

675
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:46,100
It's okay.

676
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:46,670
Give me.

677
00:24:46,910 --> 00:24:47,230
Mom.

678
00:24:47,230 --> 00:24:48,540
My cooking isn't as good as yours.

679
00:24:48,540 --> 00:24:49,260
No.

680
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:51,230
Your cooking is much better than mine.

681
00:24:52,150 --> 00:24:54,300
I wish Grandma, Dad, and Mom

682
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:55,910
good health, good luck,

683
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:57,670
peace, and harmony.

684
00:24:57,675 --> 00:24:58,630
Happy Chinese New Year.

685
00:24:58,825 --> 00:25:00,950
- Happy Chinese New Year.
- What a sweet talker.

686
00:25:01,020 --> 00:25:02,100
Thank you, Huan'er.

687
00:25:02,990 --> 00:25:03,340
Here.

688
00:25:03,580 --> 00:25:04,630
New year, new beginnings.

689
00:25:05,150 --> 00:25:06,910
Your dad and I have
no other hope for you.

690
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:09,340
We only wish you

691
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:11,190
good health and peace in the new year.

692
00:25:11,990 --> 00:25:12,300
Here.

693
00:25:12,975 --> 00:25:14,125
Happy Chinese New Year.

694
00:25:14,190 --> 00:25:15,425
Happy Chinese New Year.

695
00:25:17,540 --> 00:25:19,100
Try your dad's cooking.

696
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:40,225
Happy Chinese New Year.

697
00:25:40,275 --> 00:25:41,675
Happy Chinese New Year, Mom.

698
00:26:09,900 --> 00:26:11,350
I forgot to get the dumplings.

699
00:26:11,350 --> 00:26:12,670
Mom, let me get them.

700
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:14,910
Huan'er has grown up.

701
00:26:15,625 --> 00:26:17,175
You take care of your mom now.

702
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:18,740
No, there's still a long way off.

703
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:20,190
She's forgetful and careless.

704
00:26:23,125 --> 00:26:26,425
(Dr. Qian, I heard about your situation.
It's best to get a biopsy done soon.)

705
00:26:40,375 --> 00:26:41,525
(Dr. Qian.)

706
00:26:41,625 --> 00:26:43,225
(I heard about your situation.)

707
00:26:43,275 --> 00:26:45,650
(It's best to get a biopsy done
after Chinese New Year.)

708
00:26:45,870 --> 00:26:47,775
(It's better to do it
sooner rather than later.)

709
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:56,390
Mom.

710
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:57,500
Mom.

711
00:26:58,540 --> 00:26:59,020
Mom.

712
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,190
Why did you get up so early?

713
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,400
You didn't even wake me up.

714
00:27:01,450 --> 00:27:01,975
Jeez.

715
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:02,990
I'm used to it.

716
00:27:04,430 --> 00:27:05,950
Did Chen Lei make breakfast for you?

717
00:27:06,340 --> 00:27:07,540
No, I made it.

718
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,390
Why didn't Chen Lei do it for you?

719
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:10,540
He went to the temple

720
00:27:10,820 --> 00:27:11,470
to pray.

721
00:27:14,100 --> 00:27:14,430
Okay.

722
00:27:14,820 --> 00:27:16,390
I'll leave him alone then.

723
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:19,060
Are you watching TV?

724
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:20,260
It's mute.

725
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:23,100
I'm just watching for fun.

726
00:27:23,125 --> 00:27:25,060
You're still asleep.
I was worried I'd disturb you.

727
00:27:25,060 --> 00:27:25,780
It's okay.

728
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:26,950
Huan'er is still asleep.

729
00:27:27,950 --> 00:27:28,950
Look at the time.

730
00:27:29,450 --> 00:27:30,900
She's still lying in bed at this age.

731
00:27:30,910 --> 00:27:31,740
It's time to wake up.

732
00:27:32,540 --> 00:27:34,400
Why are you also acting like a child?

733
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,580
I never grow up.

734
00:27:35,625 --> 00:27:36,825
You're arguing with her?

735
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:43,150
Mom.

736
00:27:43,430 --> 00:27:43,910
Grandma.

737
00:27:45,275 --> 00:27:46,619
Happy Chinese New Year.

738
00:27:46,620 --> 00:27:48,650
- Happy Chinese New Year.
- Happy Chinese New Year.

739
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,340
Look.

740
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:51,150
Mom.

741
00:27:52,075 --> 00:27:53,260
She's already in university,

742
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,900
yet you're still giving her
a red envelope.

743
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:56,775
- Thank you, Grandma.
- It's Chinese New Year.

744
00:27:57,100 --> 00:27:58,190
Look what this is.

745
00:27:58,740 --> 00:27:59,870
This is yours.

746
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:00,670
I don't want it.

747
00:28:00,670 --> 00:28:01,100
Take it.

748
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:02,780
It's from me.

749
00:28:02,870 --> 00:28:03,740
It's from me. Take it.

750
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,425
Happy Chinese New Year.

751
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:06,475
Happy Chinese New Year.

752
00:28:06,950 --> 00:28:08,020
You're all my darlings.

753
00:28:10,430 --> 00:28:11,340
Third Uncle's calling.

754
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:12,975
It must wish you
a happy Chinese New Year.

755
00:28:12,975 --> 00:28:13,825
Here. Answer it.

756
00:28:13,870 --> 00:28:14,275
Okay.

757
00:28:14,670 --> 00:28:15,580
Let me take the call.

758
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:16,390
Hello?

759
00:28:16,870 --> 00:28:17,780
Hey.

760
00:28:18,150 --> 00:28:19,710
Happy Chinese New Year.

761
00:28:20,710 --> 00:28:21,780
Is everything okay at home?

762
00:28:24,390 --> 00:28:24,990
I'm fine.

763
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:26,230
I'm in good health.

764
00:28:30,990 --> 00:28:32,390
It's the new year.

765
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:33,390
I wish you

766
00:28:33,710 --> 00:28:35,740
health and happiness.

767
00:28:37,475 --> 00:28:38,625
What's the matter?

768
00:28:38,650 --> 00:28:40,000
You took Grandma's red envelope

769
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:40,850
but not mine?

770
00:28:42,710 --> 00:28:43,190
Mom.

771
00:28:45,390 --> 00:28:47,100
Yesterday,

772
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:49,100
I saw your text message.

773
00:28:52,050 --> 00:28:53,670
It's okay. It's just a minor surgery.

774
00:28:53,670 --> 00:28:54,580
Don't worry.

775
00:28:56,740 --> 00:28:58,060
It's Chinese New Year. Be happy.

776
00:28:58,100 --> 00:28:59,020
Don't let Grandma know.

777
00:28:59,020 --> 00:28:59,670
You hear me?

778
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:00,540
Don't overthink.

779
00:29:03,100 --> 00:29:03,990
How did it go?

780
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:05,190
How is he?

781
00:29:05,390 --> 00:29:06,150
He's okay.

782
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:07,710
All his family is well.

783
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:08,630
Great.

784
00:29:09,100 --> 00:29:09,670
Huan'er.

785
00:29:09,870 --> 00:29:11,375
Brush your teeth. It's time to eat.

786
00:29:11,375 --> 00:29:12,075
Grandma made it.

787
00:29:12,100 --> 00:29:12,990
Yes, eat breakfast.

788
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:13,540
Mom.

789
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:14,580
Here.

790
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:15,050
Hurry.

791
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:16,500
I

792
00:29:16,630 --> 00:29:17,740
bought you a hat.

793
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:20,060
I saw your hat was old that day.

794
00:29:20,375 --> 00:29:22,425
I want to take you shopping
this afternoon.

795
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:25,190
(That was the first time I realized)

796
00:29:25,870 --> 00:29:27,740
(that learning to keep secrets)

797
00:29:28,470 --> 00:29:29,870
(is an important lesson)

798
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:33,020
(in growing up.)

799
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:46,710
What's wrong?

800
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:48,950
It's Chinese New Year,
yet you look upset.

801
00:29:53,975 --> 00:29:55,075
What's wrong?

802
00:29:56,950 --> 00:29:57,580
My mom

803
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:02,020
was diagnosed with a tumor.

804
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:23,580
Is it benign or malignant?

805
00:30:25,825 --> 00:30:26,975
I have no idea.

806
00:30:27,990 --> 00:30:29,150
She needs an operation.

807
00:30:33,190 --> 00:30:34,430
Do you think my mom

808
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:35,870
would...

809
00:30:35,990 --> 00:30:36,950
It must be benign.

810
00:30:38,975 --> 00:30:40,430
You don't have the results yet.

811
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:41,775
Don't scare yourself first.

812
00:30:42,825 --> 00:30:43,575
Sure.

813
00:30:45,870 --> 00:30:46,230
Yes.

814
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:00,670
Grandma.

815
00:32:08,100 --> 00:32:08,910
It's late.

816
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:10,780
Why are you still awake?

817
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:14,190
I'm going through
your mom's photo album.

818
00:32:17,150 --> 00:32:18,500
I heard your mom say

819
00:32:19,300 --> 00:32:20,390
you made this for her.

820
00:32:24,942 --> 00:32:26,245
During senior middle school.

821
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,340
Huan'er has grown up

822
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:41,710
and is sensible.

823
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:50,580
It'll be fine.

824
00:33:03,020 --> 00:33:03,820
(At that moment,)

825
00:33:05,100 --> 00:33:06,390
(I suddenly understood)

826
00:33:07,670 --> 00:33:09,020
(that Grandma and I)

827
00:33:09,950 --> 00:33:11,457
(are keeping the same secret)

828
00:33:11,457 --> 00:33:12,540
(for each other.)

829
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:15,300
(She's a mother.)

830
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:17,870
(A mother who's willing)

831
00:33:17,870 --> 00:33:19,740
(to pretend that she knows nothing.)

832
00:33:20,870 --> 00:33:22,540
(Because she doesn't want)

833
00:33:23,190 --> 00:33:24,710
(her daughter)

834
00:33:25,580 --> 00:33:26,950
(to worry about her)

835
00:33:27,731 --> 00:33:29,148
(while suffering from illness.)

836
00:34:08,540 --> 00:34:08,910
Mom.

837
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,680
This is the pork elbow
I braised for you.

838
00:34:10,691 --> 00:34:12,140
Remember to put it in the refrigerator

839
00:34:12,140 --> 00:34:12,954
after you're home.

840
00:34:12,965 --> 00:34:13,857
Or it will go bad.

841
00:34:14,350 --> 00:34:16,270
This is a new type of hypoglycemic drug.

842
00:34:17,060 --> 00:34:18,180
I've written out

843
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:19,660
the instructions for you.

844
00:34:19,990 --> 00:34:22,180
The frequency a day and the dosage.

845
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:23,430
Got it.

846
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:25,100
I'm not senile yet.

847
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:26,390
Mom.

848
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:28,620
I have to rush to work

849
00:34:28,750 --> 00:34:29,790
and still need to clean up,

850
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:31,576
so I won't be sending you off.

851
00:34:32,024 --> 00:34:32,952
Don't worry about me.

852
00:34:33,140 --> 00:34:34,390
I have my son-in-law.

853
00:34:34,390 --> 00:34:35,790
Yes, I'm here. Don't worry.

854
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:37,220
Bye.

855
00:34:38,870 --> 00:34:39,470
Huan'er.

856
00:34:39,660 --> 00:34:40,310
Grandma.

857
00:34:42,870 --> 00:34:43,830
I will miss you.

858
00:34:44,470 --> 00:34:45,700
I will call you.

859
00:34:45,736 --> 00:34:46,824
Take good care of yourself.

860
00:34:46,824 --> 00:34:47,180
Sure.

861
00:34:47,368 --> 00:34:47,870
Don't worry.

862
00:34:49,140 --> 00:34:49,500
Mom.

863
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:52,540
You must pay attention to your health.

864
00:34:52,910 --> 00:34:53,390
And

865
00:34:53,768 --> 00:34:54,870
if you're not feeling well,

866
00:34:54,910 --> 00:34:55,620
let me know.

867
00:34:56,270 --> 00:34:58,060
I'll go back to visit you
if I have time.

868
00:34:58,750 --> 00:34:59,140
Sure.

869
00:34:59,830 --> 00:35:01,224
Take good care of yourself too.

870
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,168
Don't worry.

871
00:35:02,310 --> 00:35:03,310
Don't let me worry.

872
00:35:05,830 --> 00:35:06,540
Bye.

873
00:35:08,536 --> 00:35:10,040
Huan'er, no need to see me off.

874
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:11,790
Dad, let me see you guys off.

875
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:12,350
Alright.

876
00:35:12,350 --> 00:35:13,220
Your grandma said no,

877
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:14,152
so don't see us off.

878
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:15,910
Dad.

879
00:35:16,020 --> 00:35:17,140
Be safe.

880
00:35:18,968 --> 00:35:19,768
Go back inside.

881
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:51,990
Mom.

882
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:53,140
Stop crying.

883
00:35:53,768 --> 00:35:54,750
You're wasting water.

884
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:56,500
I'm not crying.

885
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:26,830
Well...

886
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:30,100
Don't be nervous
about the operation tomorrow.

887
00:36:30,830 --> 00:36:31,990
The test results will be fine.

888
00:36:32,620 --> 00:36:33,310
I'm not nervous.

889
00:36:33,688 --> 00:36:35,112
You're the one who's nervous.

890
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:36,700
Why would I be nervous?

891
00:36:37,140 --> 00:36:38,168
You're nervous.

892
00:36:38,470 --> 00:36:38,790
Look.

893
00:36:39,096 --> 00:36:40,270
Even my hands are sweating.

894
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:41,660
Look, it's all sweat.

895
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:43,390
Sweat...

896
00:36:45,350 --> 00:36:46,350
Alright.

897
00:36:46,830 --> 00:36:47,750
It's late.

898
00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:48,990
Go home.

899
00:36:50,140 --> 00:36:50,870
There's no rush.

900
00:36:51,870 --> 00:36:52,792
People will see you.

901
00:36:52,808 --> 00:36:54,456
Let me stay with you for a while longer.

902
00:36:54,470 --> 00:36:54,790
Here.

903
00:37:25,870 --> 00:37:26,390
You're here.

904
00:37:36,424 --> 00:37:37,368
How did it go?

905
00:37:40,950 --> 00:37:41,990
We don't know yet.

906
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:44,220
We'll only know the final result

907
00:37:45,470 --> 00:37:47,140
after the biopsy

908
00:37:47,672 --> 00:37:48,990
following tomorrow's operation.

909
00:37:57,192 --> 00:37:59,032
You must have starved the whole day.

910
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,792
Have some food.

911
00:38:03,990 --> 00:38:04,390
Thank you.

912
00:38:20,392 --> 00:38:22,408
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

913
00:38:23,870 --> 00:38:24,950
It isn't your fault.

914
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:28,830
Aunt Lina will be fine.

915
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:43,780
(Family Members Are Not Allowed Inside)

916
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:50,460
(In Operation)

917
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:55,752
How did it go?

918
00:39:56,750 --> 00:39:57,140
Yifan.

919
00:39:57,140 --> 00:39:58,430
Why are you here?

920
00:39:58,456 --> 00:39:59,700
I should be here. We're family.

921
00:39:59,752 --> 00:40:00,952
How long has she been in there?

922
00:40:00,968 --> 00:40:01,500
(In Operation)

923
00:40:01,500 --> 00:40:02,350
It's been a long time.

924
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:03,270
I don't know either.

925
00:40:03,384 --> 00:40:03,830
It's over.

926
00:40:04,056 --> 00:40:04,700
It's over, Dad.

927
00:40:05,784 --> 00:40:06,350
This door...

928
00:40:06,350 --> 00:40:06,910
No rush.

929
00:40:06,968 --> 00:40:07,750
It'll be over soon.

930
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:08,950
Doctor.

931
00:40:09,192 --> 00:40:10,008
How did it go?

932
00:40:10,040 --> 00:40:10,968
Everything went well.

933
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:12,660
Family members can wait in the ward.

934
00:40:12,990 --> 00:40:14,660
Judging from the tumor removed,

935
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:15,912
there should be no problem.

936
00:40:15,912 --> 00:40:17,890
But we still have to wait
for the biopsy results.

937
00:40:18,008 --> 00:40:18,536
Alright.

938
00:40:18,750 --> 00:40:19,700
Thank you.

939
00:40:19,736 --> 00:40:20,470
Thank you, Doctor.

940
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:21,390
Don't mention it. Go.

941
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:22,408
- Thank you.
- Okay.

942
00:40:24,310 --> 00:40:25,950
Dad, she's fine.

943
00:40:26,830 --> 00:40:27,660
Look, I told you

944
00:40:27,660 --> 00:40:28,700
it's a minor operation.

945
00:40:28,744 --> 00:40:30,296
Yet you still came to accompany me.

946
00:40:30,312 --> 00:40:31,500
You make me very nervous.

947
00:40:31,790 --> 00:40:32,270
Uncle.

948
00:40:32,270 --> 00:40:32,660
I...

949
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:34,410
I'll buy you some drinks.

950
00:40:34,410 --> 00:40:35,220
No need, Uncle. No.

951
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:36,088
No need. Stand here.

952
00:40:36,088 --> 00:40:37,352
- It's okay.
- There's no need.

953
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:45,500
(Dad is still the same as before.)

954
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:46,990
(The more nervous he is,)

955
00:40:47,016 --> 00:40:48,660
(the more he acts like he doesn't care.)

956
00:40:49,390 --> 00:40:51,100
(I don't know if it's to comfort others)

957
00:40:51,430 --> 00:40:52,750
(or himself.)

958
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,310
Slow down.

959
00:40:57,310 --> 00:40:58,390
Mom, slow down.

960
00:40:59,020 --> 00:40:59,620
It's okay.

961
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,350
Slow down.

962
00:41:00,350 --> 00:41:01,100
It's okay.

963
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:02,060
Let Huan'er help you.

964
00:41:02,060 --> 00:41:02,910
Let me do it myself.

965
00:41:03,310 --> 00:41:04,750
I'm not a porcelain doll.

966
00:41:04,950 --> 00:41:05,540
Jeez.

967
00:41:10,830 --> 00:41:11,100
Chen.

968
00:41:11,750 --> 00:41:12,320
Look.

969
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:13,580
Xichi is capable.

970
00:41:13,976 --> 00:41:15,688
Doesn't he look like our son-in-law?

971
00:41:19,310 --> 00:41:20,100
Son-in-law?

972
00:41:20,140 --> 00:41:21,700
Stop playing matchmaker.

973
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,060
He's handsome

974
00:41:23,064 --> 00:41:24,696
and has no shortage of girlfriends.

975
00:41:24,700 --> 00:41:26,140
They're good buddies.

976
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:27,390
Son-in-law?

977
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:30,790
Xichi.

978
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,830
Sorry to have bothered you recently.

979
00:41:33,208 --> 00:41:34,700
I can't take care of you all for now.

980
00:41:35,080 --> 00:41:36,830
You two will be back in school
in two days.

981
00:41:36,990 --> 00:41:37,750
Help me

982
00:41:37,830 --> 00:41:38,950
take care of Huan'er.

983
00:41:39,224 --> 00:41:40,232
Aunt Lina, don't worry.

984
00:41:40,248 --> 00:41:41,250
Leave Chen Huan'er to me.

985
00:41:43,350 --> 00:41:44,060
Here, get up.

986
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,990
I'll do it myself.

987
00:41:46,020 --> 00:41:46,870
Don't touch me.

988
00:41:46,870 --> 00:41:47,540
Let me.

989
00:41:48,910 --> 00:41:49,750
Okay, go.

990
00:41:50,180 --> 00:41:51,180
Don't force yourself.

991
00:41:51,390 --> 00:41:52,660
Don't touch me.

992
00:41:52,660 --> 00:41:53,528
Let me do it myself.

993
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:54,904
I know. Let me help you.

994
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:18,450
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

995
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:25,320
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

996
00:42:27,090 --> 00:42:32,440
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

997
00:42:32,750 --> 00:42:38,240
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

998
00:42:40,830 --> 00:42:45,850
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

999
00:42:47,640 --> 00:42:52,880
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

1000
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:59,900
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

1001
00:43:00,360 --> 00:43:05,860
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

1002
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:11,020
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

1003
00:43:11,020 --> 00:43:16,010
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

1004
00:43:16,140 --> 00:43:19,570
♪And full of life♪

1005
00:43:20,860 --> 00:43:24,320
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

1006
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:29,430
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

1007
00:43:29,690 --> 00:43:34,080
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

1008
00:43:34,580 --> 00:43:38,480
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

1009
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:43,420
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

1010
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:46,210
♪To know right from wrong♪

1011
00:43:48,120 --> 00:43:51,650
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

1012
00:43:51,650 --> 00:43:54,900
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

1013
00:43:55,060 --> 00:44:00,820
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

1014
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:05,840
♪At just the right time♪

